{"tid":1459232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口號要變 賽後檢討 展望未來","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:03:43.000Z","uid":85051,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05b66f34ac6b995b47a6fa35a1b286c9f79415e4","tid":1459232,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"利申：純個人意見，無任何意圖煽動、支持犯罪活動，內容只供學術討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>口號</ins></span><br />\n- 暫時停用「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用「五大訴求，缺一不可，不傷不被捕，不割不篤灰」</span><br />\n<br />\n原因：今日一役，已經睇到對面戰術成功：引起內鬥。對面最恐懼係我地戰線統一，因為佢地無得逐個擊破。<br />\n<br />\n效果：加強鞏固意識，勇武和理繼續緊密合作！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>檢討</ins></span><br />\n好：<br />\n1. 安全離去<br />\n2. 展示民意<br />\n3. 無人傷亡<br />\n<br />\n有待改善之處：<br />\n1. 互相指罵 <br />\n（改善方法：「我地下次要做得更好」）<br />\n無人鍾意聽指責嘅說話，鼓勵先可以激勵士氣，並可以心平氣和討論。<br />\n<br />\n2. 尊重他人決定<br />\n（改善方法：盡可能只已FC提供資訊）<br />\n每個人都要對自己決定負責。可以分享意見俾其他，但最終決定權係每個人自己手上。<br />\n<br />\n3. Fact Check方法<br />\n（改善方法：相中要有資料來源嘅證明、時間、日期）<br />\n今日有好資料有來源，但無人有資料去證明翻來源，咁會造成資訊泛濫。我地要嚴格查考資料真偽，可能費時，但資料係屬實，一定有資料去追查到來源。來源吻合，當然係真。所以小心使用fact check呢隻字。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">展望未來</span></ins><br />\n1. 減低傷亡率<br />\n<br />\n2. 民意戰擴大版圖<br />\n<br />\n3. 勇武同和理非嘅合作共識<br />\n<br />\n4. 風向<br />\n<br />\n希望各位由連登呢度做起"},{"pid":"a2e8bec51150f9d0af0a55d78ae3bc20e3d3b4fc","tid":1459232,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"9f0c84f7123a02c94174f6341104d3a6fffcde2a","tid":1459232,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:39:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48a38538035d553e5fa091f00765c9de39b0ae29","tid":1459232,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"機場見"},{"pid":"7ffd8ae8091cb7fabdd1a9e52330697384e50f6c","tid":1459232,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0df39c0ba11f5b02ad462b08f101d37db510fcf4","tid":1459232,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e51cd82576dce5f364e05b99a95841d2cbfaa7b","tid":1459232,"uid":36761,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48a38538035d553e5fa091f00765c9de39b0ae29","tid":1459232,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"機場見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"唔可以100%癱瘓, 記住呢個重點<br />\n最理想70-80%癱瘓<br />\n100%癱瘓=無服務=無遊客旅客無職員<br />\n黑警到時落閘放狗, 瘋狂掃射"},{"pid":"46a73ef17405849e8a1918b396e32343c7432488","tid":1459232,"uid":294930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:45:21.000Z","msg":"同意！ 特別係2。"},{"pid":"36b9fb584f15002ce180869e3fac0ee83e8d8b35","tid":1459232,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:54:07.000Z","msg":"why not both,兩個都有佢嘅作用，揀時候用"},{"pid":"c7752933a49a29ceaf12bfc41a78f183d96e1027","tid":1459232,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7406bca929ca9fdff1b4440439f64bd79e089602","tid":1459232,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"25b6759cac4d2292c412ed1b973957485101557a","tid":1459232,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d0d3e85585c2453701279ea86c972da35568711e","tid":1459232,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5e3